reviewText: This a great video on elk hunting. The Petersen's staff are very professional, and the video contains some very exciting hunts which are presented in a very informative manner. It is a very informative, but enjoyable video. The reason which it is different from many other video is the lack of immature behavior you find in other videos. All in all, a great video to watch.
Easy gift for overseas - anything light and postable... kids will love it
This  is a gift for a son who hunts. Pleased with the service of 'Fast" at this Christmas time. Thank you much!
